About the Opportunity

Horizon Digital is partnering with a major organisation on a high-impact engineering project and is looking for an experienced Senior C++ Developer to join the team.

This is a hands-on role focused on building and enhancing a real-time system operating in a complex, high-availability environment. You’ll be contributing to software where performance, responsiveness, and reliability genuinely matter. 

The Role

You’ll work on a live C++ system that processes operational data in real time, helping to improve performance, scalability, and overall system capability.

This role would suit someone who enjoys solving technical problems in production environments, is comfortable working with existing systems, and brings a strong engineering mindset to complex challenges. 

Key Responsibilities

Develop and maintain core C++ components within a real-time production system
