This role is responsible for undertaking Identity Gateway (IDG) design, configuration, and integrations, within a federal government cloud environment. It ensures the end-to-end technical delivery of Identity Management & Access.

Experience Required

Configuration and customisation of the Identity Gateway tool.
Integration of Identity Gateway, with the departmental source and consumer systems.
Experience with DevOps build & release processes and automation scripts.
Detailed design and as-built documentation.
